smadays=30
mmadays=130
lmadays=200

def RSI(series, period):
    delta = series.diff().dropna()
    u = delta * 0
    d = u.copy()
    u[delta > 0] = delta[delta > 0]
    d[delta < 0] = -delta[delta < 0]
    u[u.index[period-1]] = np.mean( u[:period] ) #first value is sum of avg gains
    u = u.drop(u.index[:(period-1)])
    d[d.index[period-1]] = np.mean( d[:period] ) #first value is sum of avg losses
    d = d.drop(d.index[:(period-1)])
    rs = pd.stats.moments.ewma(u, com=period-1, adjust=False) / \
    pd.stats.moments.ewma(d, com=period-1, adjust=False)
    return 100 - 100 / (1 + rs)

def ATR(df, n):  
    i = 0  
    TR_l = [0]  
    while i < df.index[-1]:  
        TR = max(df.get_value(i + 1, 'high'), df.get_value(i, 'close')) - min(df.get_value(i + 1, 'low'), df.get_value(i, 'close'))  
        TR_l.append(TR)  
        i = i + 1  
    TR_s = pd.Series(TR_l)  
    ATR = pd.Series(pd.ewma(TR_s, span = n, min_periods = n), name = 'atr')  
    df = df.join(ATR)
    return df

def rollingRankBottleneck (array):
    return array.size + 1 - bottleneck.rankdata(array)[-1]

                rsiH=rsiH+1

                belowma=belowma+1                
            if globals()[key].loc[X,'close'] > globals()[key].loc[X,'lma']:
                abovema=abovema+1
            if globals()[key].loc[X,'at52high']:

                Nat52low=Nat52low+1
            if globals()[key].loc[X,'Up_Dn'] == 1:
                u_count=u_count+1
            if globals()[key].loc[X,'Up_Dn'] == 0:    
                d_count=d_count+1
    #print X, XY, AB
    merged.at[X, 'rsiL'] = rsiL
    merged.at[X, 'rsiH'] = rsiH
    merged.at[X, 'belowma'] = belowma
    merged.at[X, 'abovema'] = abovema
    merged.at[X, 'total_tickers'] = total_tickers
    merged.at[X, 'Nat52WH'] = Nat52WH
    merged.at[X, 'Nat52low'] = Nat52low
    merged.at[X, 'u_count'] = u_count
    merged.at[X, 'd_count'] = d_count
# holidays have zero traded quantity, but not accounted by pandas bdate_range
merged.drop(merged[merged.total_tickers == 0].index, inplace=True)

merged['rsiHL'] = (merged['rsiH'] / merged['rsiL'])
merged['rsiH-L'] = (merged['rsiH'] - merged['rsiL'])
merged['rsiHpct'] = (merged['rsiH'] / merged['total_tickers'])*100
merged['rsiLpct'] = (merged['rsiL'] / merged['total_tickers'])*100
merged['rsiHLpct'] = (merged['rsiHpct'] / merged['rsiLpct'])
merged['rsiH-Lpct'] = (merged['rsiHpct'] - merged['rsiLpct'])
merged['MA_osc'] = (merged['abovema'] / merged['belowma'])
merged['MA_Hpct'] = (merged['abovema'] / merged['total_tickers'])*100
merged['MA_Lpct'] = (merged['belowma'] / merged['total_tickers'])*100
merged['HL_osc'] = (merged['Nat52WH'] / merged['Nat52low'])
merged['HL_Hpct'] = (merged['Nat52WH'] / merged['total_tickers'])*100
merged['HL_Lpct'] = (merged['Nat52low'] / merged['total_tickers'])*100
merged['pos_neg'] = merged['n50_d2chg'] >= 0
merged.pos_neg = merged.pos_neg.astype(int)
merged['rsiHL_5sma']=merged.rolling(window=5)['rsiHL'].mean()
merged['HL_osc_5sma']=merged.rolling(window=5)['HL_osc'].mean()
merged['RANA'] = (merged['u_count'] - merged['d_count'])/(merged['u_count'] + merged['d_count'])
merged['RANA_ema_slow']=merged['RANA'].ewm(span=5,min_periods=5,adjust=False).mean()
merged['RANA_ema_fast']=merged['RANA'].ewm(span=10,min_periods=10,adjust=False).mean()
merged['mcc_osc']=merged['RANA_ema_fast']-merged['RANA_ema_slow']
merged['rsiLpctsma']=merged.rolling(window=5)['rsiLpct'].mean()

# if stock has buy signal & posistion is not open, then add first unit, based on cash posistion, stop price and risk.
#         update posistions table, cash posistion
# if stock has buy signal & posistion is already open, then add additional unit, based on cash posistion, 
#         price-chg since first-unit-entry to last price, not yet max units, unit size based on first-unit-size %
#         pyraminding example = every 15% rise since first unit, we will add 25% more to quantity till we hit 10 units max
# if stock has sell signal & posistion is open, then exit and move stock to closed_posistions, update cash
#

# risk per trade

# pyramiding

# 25% of initial unit size

Risk_Equity=0

def updt_opeq(a):
    Open_Equity=0
    Risk_Equity=0
    Closed_Equity=0
    Total_Equity=0
    open_qty=0
    close=0
    T_Cash=0
    # if there is no trade take last known cash value
    if len(pos_dict[a].index) > 0:
        T_Cash=equity.query('Date <= @a').tail(1).values.tolist()[0][4]
        Closed_Equity=equity.query('Date <= @a').tail(1).values.tolist()[0][2]
    for MNO in pd.unique(pos_dict[a]['Ticker'].values.ravel()):
        #
        open_qty=pos_dict[a].query('Ticker == @MNO').tail(1).values.tolist()[0][7]
        close=globals()[MNO].query('date < @a')['close'].tail(1).values.tolist()[0]
        #close=stock_dict[MNO].query('date < @a')['close'].tail(1).values.tolist()[0]
        #Open_Equity_pos=pos_dict[a].query('Ticker == @MNO').tail(1).values.tolist()[0][7]*stock_dict['MNO'].query('date < @a')['close'].tail(1).values.tolist()[0]
        Open_Equity_pos=open_qty*close
        Open_Equity=Open_Equity_pos+Open_Equity
        Risk_Equity=Risk_Equity+pos_dict[a].query('Ticker == @MNO').tail(1).values.tolist()[0][8]
        #Closed_Equity=Closed_Eq
    Total_Equity=Open_Equity+T_Cash
    return a, Risk_Equity, Open_Equity, Closed_Equity, T_Cash, Total_Equity


OOO = [(k) for k,v in pos_dict.iteritems()]

    p = Pool(16)
    results=[]
    # this will spawn updt_opeq for each value in OOO list
    results1=p.map_async(updt_opeq, OOO)

mask[np.triu_indices_from(mask)] = True
# Set up the matplotlib figure
f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 9))

# Generate a custom diverging colormap
cmap = sns.diverging_palette(220, 10, as_cmap=True)

# Draw the heatmap with the mask and correct aspect ratio
heatmap = sns.heatmap(corr, mask=mask, cmap=cmap, vmax=0.3, center=0,
            square=True, linewidths=.5, cbar_kws={"shrink": .5})

heatmap.set_yticklabels(heatmap.get_yticklabels(), rotation=0,fontsize = 8)
heatmap.set_xticklabels(heatmap.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45,fontsize = 8)
